  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.poster.avif?t=1759785274\" width=626 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.webm?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.mp4?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floodlight</strong> is a short horror game where you play as a broke college student who just moved into a crappy apartment, which should have been fine if it weren't for the massively bright light that gets turned on every night, directed straight at your apartment's window...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring an immersive, atmospheric experience with photorealistic graphics, discover the truth about this mysterious apartment by exploring the environment around you. Talk to the neighbors to find out what is going on, but you may just end up with more questions than answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.poster.avif?t=1759785274\" width=626 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.webm?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.mp4?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Third-person camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the environment to unlock the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom in to investigate closely and find clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manual saving and reloading whenever you deem necessary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 30-40 minutes</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.poster.avif?t=1759785274\" width=626 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.webm?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/252b5487ac461d26700d87204d34770c.mp4?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Floodlight</strong> is a short horror game where you play as a broke college student who just moved into a crappy apartment, which should have been fine if it weren't for the massively bright light that gets turned on every night, directed straight at your apartment's window...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring an immersive, atmospheric experience with photorealistic graphics, discover the truth about this mysterious apartment by exploring the environment around you. Talk to the neighbors to find out what is going on, but you may just end up with more questions than answers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.poster.avif?t=1759785274\" width=626 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.webm?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3429150/extras/0e4a1e1b1a443cc2459f29f69bb831fb.mp4?t=1759785274\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Main features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Third-person camera</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the environment to unlock the story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Zoom in to investigate closely and find clues</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manual saving and reloading whenever you deem necessary</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Estimated playtime: 30-40 minutes</p></li></ul>",
